---
<section id="process" class="section-pad">
  
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);">
    <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-4xl);">How <span class="text-accent">It Works</span></h2>
    <p style="margin: 0 auto; font-size: var(--text-lg); max-width: 60ch;">Our rapid implementation process ensures that your business starts seeing results immediately with minimal effort.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-lg); max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
    
    <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-md); align-items: flex-start;">
      <div style="flex-shrink: 0; width: 48px; height: 48px; background: var(--color-accent); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 800; font-size: var(--text-xl);">1</div>
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-2xl); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Free Consultation</h3>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-base); margin: 0;">Talk with a professional systems engineer (typically $500+/hr) to thoroughly discuss your project requirements and objectives.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-md); align-items: flex-start;">
      <div style="flex-shrink: 0; width: 48px; height: 48px; background: var(--color-accent); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 800; font-size: var(--text-xl);">2</div>
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-2xl); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Strategy and Proposal</h3>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-base); margin: 0;">Following your consultation, we will deliver a comprehensive scope, outlining itemized steps, a detailed timeline, and budget estimates.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-md); align-items: flex-start;">
      <div style="flex-shrink: 0; width: 48px; height: 48px; background: var(--color-accent); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 800; font-size: var(--text-xl);">3</div>
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-2xl); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Implementation</h3>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-base); margin: 0;">Upon approval, our rapid implementation process ensures that your business starts seeing explosive growth immediately.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

</section>
